message.content:
cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.SY

Reasoning: 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on learning policies for high-dimensional control of a multi-fingered gripper, which is a challenging system to control.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes a novel approach to self-supervised learning using a curriculum-based sampling strategy.
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is relevant as the policies are learned from visual information.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the paper proposes a new approach to learning policies for high-dimensional control.
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is relevant as the paper focuses on learning policies for controlling a complex system.
